text:
I'm in the same situation as when I wear a mask...
My identity shouldn't be revealed.

Haha, what's that!
You're just covering your eyes with your own hands!

I don't have fancy masks like Yuika's...
It's a DIY mask.

What kind of prank do you want to pull off without being
recognized? It's like I'm the suspect with that eye-covering stance.

If you want to joke around, you'll have to use your
head a bit more, okay? Like Mitsumine.
